00:00:16.800 --> 00:00:19.440 line:80%
-What's wrong?
-Stop.

00:00:19.520 --> 00:00:20.880 line:80%
-Say that again.
-Enough.

00:00:20.960 --> 00:00:22.200 line:80%
-Say that again.
-Step back.

00:00:22.280 --> 00:00:23.880 line:80%
Enough. Step back.

00:00:24.680 --> 00:00:25.680 line:80%
Let them go this once.

00:00:26.720 --> 00:00:27.880 line:80%
Those prisoners,

00:00:27.960 --> 00:00:29.880 line:80%
our Yanzhou army shed blood
and sweat to capture them.

00:00:30.400 --> 00:00:32.200 line:80%
What right do you Jizhou troops have
to take half?

00:00:32.279 --> 00:00:34.160 line:80%
-Exactly.
-What right do you have?

00:00:34.240 --> 00:00:34.920 line:80%
What right?

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:38.160 line:80%
Captain Fan and our Military Administrator
are deeply in love.

00:00:38.240 --> 00:00:40.280 line:80%
-Right.
-Soon they'll be family.

00:00:40.360 --> 00:00:42.200 line:80%
Half?

00:00:42.720 --> 00:00:44.480 line:80%
You should give us all of them.

00:00:44.560 --> 00:00:46.080 line:80%
It's only right.

00:00:46.160 --> 00:00:47.200 line:80%
-Exactly.
-Only right.

00:00:47.280 --> 00:00:48.480 line:80%
Shut up!

00:00:49.200 --> 00:00:50.040 line:80%
Nonsense!

00:00:50.760 --> 00:00:53.000 line:80%
Captain Fan already has a husband.

00:00:53.080 --> 00:00:55.800 line:80%
How could she possibly fool around with
Military Administrator Li behind his back?

00:00:55.880 --> 00:00:57.280 line:80%
Bullshit!

00:00:57.360 --> 00:01:00.560 line:80%
Captain Fan's husband died
on the battlefield long ago.

00:01:01.080 --> 00:01:02.280 line:80%
Even if he were alive,

00:01:02.360 --> 00:01:05.520 line:80%
how could he compare
to our Military Administrator?

00:01:05.600 --> 00:01:06.800 line:80%
Exactly.

00:01:06.880 --> 00:01:10.320 line:80%
Wait. Isn't your Military Administrator Li
supposed to marry the Grand Princess?

00:01:10.400 --> 00:01:12.240 line:80%
So why's he tangled up with Captain Fan?

00:01:12.320 --> 00:01:14.800 line:80%
-Exactly.
-None of your damn business.

00:01:14.880 --> 00:01:17.080 line:80%
Our Military Administrator visits
Captain Fan every single day. So what?

00:01:17.160 --> 00:01:18.840 line:80%
You, on the other hand,

00:01:18.920 --> 00:01:20.640 line:80%
could it be that your master

00:01:21.160 --> 00:01:22.520 line:80%
has his eye on Captain Fan too?

00:01:22.600 --> 00:01:23.760 line:80%
-Bullshit!
-What did you say?

00:01:23.840 --> 00:01:24.640 line:80%
You got a problem?

00:01:24.720 --> 00:01:26.200 line:80%
-Then fight.
-Why did you strike first?

00:01:26.960 --> 00:01:28.160 line:80%
-Stop it!
-Let go.

00:01:28.240 --> 00:01:29.560 line:80%
-Attention!
-Watch yourselves.

00:01:29.640 --> 00:01:31.840 line:80%
PEACE AND PROSPERITY ALONG THE BORDERS

00:01:31.920 --> 00:01:33.200 line:80%
We're all brothers in arms,

00:01:34.000 --> 00:01:35.960 line:80%
yet you fight and injure
each other over prisoners.

00:01:36.680 --> 00:01:37.600 line:80%
Where are the military regulations?

00:01:38.560 --> 00:01:41.160 line:80%
Lord Li, you be the judge.

00:01:41.240 --> 00:01:43.600 line:80%
You and Captain Fan
are practically family now.

00:01:44.200 --> 00:01:46.720 line:80%
Why split the military merits so clearly?

00:01:46.800 --> 00:01:47.800 line:80%
How dare you!

00:01:48.800 --> 00:01:50.880 line:80%
Such gossip shouldn't
be spoken carelessly.

00:01:50.960 --> 00:01:53.000 line:80%
I don't care if Military Administrator Li
likes Captain Fan or not.

00:01:53.080 --> 00:01:55.320 line:80%
But taking away the military merits of our
Yanzhou warriors?

00:01:55.400 --> 00:01:56.280 line:80%
That's not acceptable.

00:01:56.360 --> 00:01:57.680 line:80%
-Right?
-So what?

00:01:57.760 --> 00:02:00.160 line:80%
-You got a problem?
-Don't you?

00:02:00.240 --> 00:02:01.240 line:80%
All troops, hear my command!

00:02:01.320 --> 00:02:02.160 line:80%
TOKEN

00:02:05.640 --> 00:02:07.480 line:80%
Captain Fan and I have known
each other since we were nothing.

00:02:08.080 --> 00:02:09.400 line:80%
Just like all of you,

00:02:09.920 --> 00:02:11.840 line:80%
we share the bond of fighting
side by side, of life and death.

00:02:12.480 --> 00:02:16.200 line:80%
Today, Captain Fan and I have sworn
to be brother and sister.

00:02:17.200 --> 00:02:18.440 line:80%
From now on,

00:02:18.520 --> 00:02:20.280 line:80%
I will treat her as my own sister.

00:02:21.600 --> 00:02:24.800 line:80%
If anyone dares to spread rumors,
stir up trouble,

00:02:25.560 --> 00:02:27.440 line:80%
or slander Captain Fan's honor again,

00:02:27.960 --> 00:02:30.600 line:80%
they will receive 30 strokes
of the military cane, as a warning to all.

00:02:30.680 --> 00:02:31.520 line:80%
-Yes, sir.
-Yes, sir.

00:02:40.240 --> 00:02:41.160 line:80%
Let's go.

00:02:49.960 --> 00:02:50.800 line:80%
Captain Fan.

00:02:50.880 --> 00:02:52.480 line:80%
YAMEN

00:02:55.160 --> 00:02:56.160 line:80%
You all go ahead.

00:02:57.720 --> 00:02:58.560 line:80%
Let's go.

00:03:03.640 --> 00:03:05.080 line:80%
Just now, calling you my sister,

00:03:05.160 --> 00:03:06.280 line:80%
that was only a temporary measure.

00:03:06.360 --> 00:03:08.080 line:80%
There are gossips in the army.

00:03:08.160 --> 00:03:10.280 line:80%
If it offended you,
please don't take it to heart.

00:03:11.160 --> 00:03:12.160 line:80%
How could I?

00:03:12.680 --> 00:03:14.840 line:80%
I've always considered you
as an elder brother.

00:03:15.520 --> 00:03:16.760 line:80%
I'm just afraid I don't deserve.

00:03:16.840 --> 00:03:19.880 line:80%
After all, I've barely read
any military books,

00:03:20.400 --> 00:03:21.520 line:80%
and I hardly know characters.

00:03:23.400 --> 00:03:25.400 line:80%
The way to know a person
lies in their inner qualities.

00:03:25.480 --> 00:03:26.720 line:80%
It has nothing to do
with reading or literacy.

00:03:27.680 --> 00:03:31.120 line:80%
Then as your sister,
I pay my courtesy to you, my brother.

00:03:32.280 --> 00:03:33.200 line:80%
Is that how it's said?

00:03:37.920 --> 00:03:40.120 line:80%
I hereby return the greetings.
That's how it's said.

00:03:41.240 --> 00:03:42.360 line:80%
Then I'll take my leave now.

00:05:26.080 --> 00:05:30.160 line:20%
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL <i>ZHU YU</i>
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

00:05:32.960 --> 00:05:34.680 line:20%
HALL OF ARMS

00:05:34.760 --> 00:05:36.720 line:20%
This is absolutely outrageous!

00:05:37.520 --> 00:05:39.200 line:80%
Even in the palace,

00:05:39.280 --> 00:05:41.760 line:80%
I've never been treated
with such disrespect.

00:05:46.040 --> 00:05:46.920 line:80%
What are you doing?

00:05:47.000 --> 00:05:49.400 line:80%
You still expect me to drink this?

00:05:49.480 --> 00:05:51.160 line:80%
No. It's been days now.

00:05:52.600 --> 00:05:54.800 line:80%
The Marquis of Wu'an hasn't returned,

00:05:54.880 --> 00:05:56.800 line:80%
and the Grand Princess won't see me.

00:05:57.600 --> 00:05:58.760 line:80%
Let me tell you.

00:05:59.280 --> 00:06:02.640 line:80%
If you keep me
waiting here like this today,

00:06:02.720 --> 00:06:05.360 line:80%
I will immediately
set out for the capital.

00:06:05.440 --> 00:06:08.560 line:80%
I'll go before His Majesty.
I'll file an imperial complaint.

00:06:10.920 --> 00:06:12.160 line:80%
What's all this commotion?

00:06:14.680 --> 00:06:18.040 line:80%
Greetings to the Grand Princess.

00:06:19.640 --> 00:06:21.560 line:80%
Your Highness cares
so deeply for the soldiers

00:06:21.640 --> 00:06:22.560 line:80%
that you haven't found a moment

00:06:22.640 --> 00:06:25.120 line:80%
to see me all these days.

00:06:25.200 --> 00:06:27.400 line:80%
How truly touching.

00:06:27.480 --> 00:06:28.400 line:80%
You may go.

00:06:31.200 --> 00:06:32.760 line:80%
I've been overwhelmed with affairs lately,

00:06:32.840 --> 00:06:34.720 line:80%
truly unable to spare a moment.

00:06:34.800 --> 00:06:36.280 line:80%
I hope you'll understand.

00:06:37.400 --> 00:06:40.680 line:80%
May I ask why you've sought me out?

00:06:40.760 --> 00:06:42.800 line:80%
Your Highness has been away
from the palace for quite some time.

00:06:42.880 --> 00:06:46.560 line:80%
His Majesty and Empress Dowager An
are deeply concerned.

00:06:46.640 --> 00:06:50.280 line:80%
So they specially sent me to come
and see how the Grand Princess is faring.

00:06:52.640 --> 00:06:54.160 line:80%
Mother and His Majesty

00:06:54.680 --> 00:06:56.840 line:80%
know that I am here,
at the northwest front,

00:06:57.720 --> 00:06:58.960 line:80%
and yet they're not angry?

00:07:02.720 --> 00:07:04.440 line:80%
Eunuch, you may as well speak directly.

00:07:05.600 --> 00:07:07.720 line:80%
Your Highness is remarkably perceptive.

00:07:07.800 --> 00:07:09.920 line:80%
Indeed, before I came,

00:07:10.000 --> 00:07:14.800 line:80%
His Majesty and Empress Dowager An
specially asked me

00:07:14.880 --> 00:07:17.600 line:80%
to convey a message to Your Highness,

00:07:18.760 --> 00:07:22.560 line:80%
"Now that the Chongzhou rebels
have been pacified,

00:07:22.640 --> 00:07:24.800 line:80%
as the whole nation celebrates,

00:07:25.400 --> 00:07:27.400 line:80%
this marriage between you and the Marquis,

00:07:27.480 --> 00:07:30.360 line:80%
-it's better sooner than later."
-What did you say?

00:07:31.560 --> 00:07:33.400 line:80%
My marriage to whom?

00:07:34.960 --> 00:07:36.600 line:80%
The Marquis of Wu'an.

00:07:37.120 --> 00:07:38.080 line:80%
Preposterous!

00:07:39.960 --> 00:07:41.120 line:80%
My imperial brother is easily swayed.

00:07:42.000 --> 00:07:44.840 line:80%
It must be you foolish servants,
dredging up old matters

00:07:44.920 --> 00:07:47.680 line:80%
and fanning the flames,
that put this idea in his head.

00:07:48.200 --> 00:07:50.840 line:80%
This marriage, I do not accept it.

00:07:54.720 --> 00:07:57.120 line:80%
Your Highness, you left the palace
for less than six months.

00:07:57.200 --> 00:08:00.480 line:80%
Since when did you learn to curse?

00:08:03.840 --> 00:08:05.640 line:80%
The Marquis of Wu'an has earned
great distinction in battle.

00:08:05.720 --> 00:08:08.880 line:80%
By any measure,
he's a match of the highest order.

00:08:09.720 --> 00:08:13.880 line:80%
Besides, this is His Majesty's decree.

00:08:13.960 --> 00:08:15.320 line:80%
Surely you're not thinking of…

00:08:16.080 --> 00:08:18.480 line:80%
defying an imperial order?

00:08:30.280 --> 00:08:31.680 line:80%
This marriage,

00:08:32.280 --> 00:08:34.680 line:80%
you'd better take it up
with the Marquis of Wu'an first.

00:08:35.800 --> 00:08:36.959 line:80%
If he agrees,

00:08:37.719 --> 00:08:39.000 line:80%
then I'll agree.

00:08:42.040 --> 00:08:43.760 line:80%
Easy enough.

00:08:44.880 --> 00:08:47.360 line:80%
I'll see to it right away.

00:08:55.200 --> 00:08:57.520 line:80%
Please convey this to His Majesty for me.

00:08:58.320 --> 00:08:59.400 line:80%
I am grateful…

00:09:00.440 --> 00:09:02.640 line:80%
for my imperial brother's care.

00:09:02.720 --> 00:09:05.800 line:80%
I'll take my leave now.

00:09:15.240 --> 00:09:16.960 line:80%
Finally got that off my chest.

00:09:19.840 --> 00:09:21.520 line:80%
HE

00:09:23.520 --> 00:09:25.760 line:80%
It's been days now.

00:09:26.280 --> 00:09:30.160 line:80%
Busy or not, the Marquis
can't keep an imperial decree waiting.

00:09:31.160 --> 00:09:33.000 line:80%
This is a military camp. Please stop here.

00:09:35.840 --> 00:09:37.000 line:80%
Fine.

00:09:37.520 --> 00:09:40.400 line:80%
Open your worthless eyes wide
and look clearly!

00:09:40.480 --> 00:09:42.640 line:80%
I have the imperial decree right here!

00:09:44.400 --> 00:09:47.800 line:80%
Let's see who dares to stop me today!

00:09:49.480 --> 00:09:50.360 line:80%
Let's go.

00:09:57.800 --> 00:09:58.920 line:80%
Stop.

00:10:01.120 --> 00:10:03.720 line:80%
I know the Marquis
is busy with official duties.

00:10:03.800 --> 00:10:05.360 line:80%
But these past few days,

00:10:05.440 --> 00:10:09.320 line:80%
you haven't found a moment to see me.

00:10:09.400 --> 00:10:12.640 line:80%
Left with no choice,
I've brought the imperial decree

00:10:12.720 --> 00:10:16.080 line:80%
and come to trouble you here myself.

00:10:18.720 --> 00:10:19.560 line:80%
Come in.

00:10:24.000 --> 00:10:24.840 line:80%
Please.

00:10:32.960 --> 00:10:35.520 line:80%
I pay my respect to the Marquis.

00:10:39.520 --> 00:10:41.120 line:80%
What urgent matter
brings you here, Eunuch?

00:10:42.240 --> 00:10:43.600 line:80%
And daring to enter a military camp

00:10:44.120 --> 00:10:45.800 line:80%
without authorization just to see me?

00:10:49.400 --> 00:10:53.480 line:80%
Marquis, this is tremendous good news!

00:10:56.760 --> 00:10:59.040 line:80%
His Majesty has issued a decree.

00:11:03.880 --> 00:11:04.760 line:80%
Marquis of Wu'an…

00:11:10.320 --> 00:11:12.880 line:80%
The Marquis need not kneel to hear it.

00:11:14.400 --> 00:11:17.200 line:80%
His Imperial Majesty decrees,
"Heaven blesses our dynasty.

00:11:17.280 --> 00:11:20.480 line:80%
Now that the Chongzhou rebels
have been vanquished

00:11:20.560 --> 00:11:23.680 line:80%
and the nation rejoices,

00:11:23.760 --> 00:11:27.000 line:80%
the marriage between the Grand Princess
and the Marquis of Wu'an should be

00:11:27.080 --> 00:11:29.600 line:80%
-concluded sooner rather than later."
-Eunuch, say no more.

00:11:30.200 --> 00:11:31.960 line:80%
Go back and tell the young emperor

00:11:32.640 --> 00:11:34.360 line:80%
that urgent matters prevent the Marquis

00:11:34.880 --> 00:11:36.320 line:80%
from receiving the decree.

00:11:36.400 --> 00:11:39.360 line:80%
Consider today's words never spoken.

00:11:40.360 --> 00:11:43.880 line:80%
And no one else here
will breathe a word of it.

00:11:45.480 --> 00:11:49.400 line:80%
I wouldn't dare commit such an act
of deceiving the emperor.

00:11:50.120 --> 00:11:55.520 line:80%
Besides, this is His Majesty's favor
toward you, Marquis.

00:11:55.600 --> 00:11:58.840 line:80%
Just nod once, that's all it takes,

00:11:58.920 --> 00:12:03.480 line:80%
and I can return to the capital
and report back to His Majesty.

00:12:05.120 --> 00:12:06.520 line:80%
But if I…

00:12:07.880 --> 00:12:09.360 line:80%
refuse to nod?

00:12:10.640 --> 00:12:11.960 line:80%
Refuse…

00:12:14.000 --> 00:12:18.880 line:80%
Marquis, are you saying
you'd defy the decree?

00:12:19.720 --> 00:12:22.560 line:80%
I wouldn't dare deceive the emperor.

00:12:24.440 --> 00:12:25.280 line:80%
Defy the decree?

00:12:32.960 --> 00:12:35.560 line:80%
Marquis. What do you think you're doing?

00:12:41.760 --> 00:12:42.880 line:80%
Marquis of Wu'an…

00:12:43.400 --> 00:12:46.840 line:80%
Are you really plotting rebellion?

00:12:53.480 --> 00:12:57.000 line:80%
The Xie family has served Dayin
loyally for a hundred years.

00:12:58.360 --> 00:13:00.400 line:80%
My father even earned the title of martyr.

00:13:02.280 --> 00:13:04.480 line:80%
I simply don't want to tarnish his name.

00:13:08.480 --> 00:13:10.360 line:80%
Go back and tell the young emperor,

00:13:11.360 --> 00:13:13.280 line:80%
if he doesn't want to sit on that throne,

00:13:14.000 --> 00:13:16.080 line:80%
I can easily find someone else
to take his place.

00:13:16.680 --> 00:13:18.120 line:80%
Seventeen years ago,

00:13:18.200 --> 00:13:20.120 line:80%
Wei Yan helped him onto the dragon throne.

00:13:21.400 --> 00:13:22.560 line:80%
Today,

00:13:23.520 --> 00:13:25.400 line:80%
I can easily pull him down.

00:13:26.240 --> 00:13:27.840 line:80%
What?

00:13:28.400 --> 00:13:29.280 line:80%
Marquis of Wu'an,

00:13:29.800 --> 00:13:32.560 line:80%
do you realize
you're threatening His Majesty?

00:13:35.200 --> 00:13:37.120 line:80%
Please, Marquis, don't kill me.

00:13:37.200 --> 00:13:40.600 line:80%
I'm just a messenger for the decree.

00:13:47.840 --> 00:13:52.120 line:80%
I merely wish for harmony
between ruler and subject.

00:13:53.240 --> 00:13:55.480 line:80%
If you misreport my words,

00:13:56.920 --> 00:13:58.560 line:80%
don't let it jeopardize matters of state.

00:14:00.440 --> 00:14:01.320 line:80%
Thank you.

00:14:01.840 --> 00:14:05.040 line:80%
Thank you, Marquis, for sparing my life.

00:14:15.680 --> 00:14:17.160 line:80%
-It's…
-Take it yourself.

00:14:27.920 --> 00:14:29.000 line:80%
Leave quickly!

00:14:29.720 --> 00:14:31.880 line:80%
Be gentle.

00:14:33.320 --> 00:14:35.320 line:80%
ARMED AND UNYIELDING

00:14:43.160 --> 00:14:44.960 line:80%
Xie Jiuheng.

00:14:45.640 --> 00:14:48.400 line:80%
Eunuch Li came here on imperial orders.

00:14:48.480 --> 00:14:51.600 line:80%
Cutting off his ear… That's practically
slapping the emperor in the face.

00:14:51.680 --> 00:14:53.080 line:80%
What now?

00:14:53.760 --> 00:14:54.720 line:80%
Are we picking a fight with the court?

00:14:57.080 --> 00:14:59.240 line:80%
The young emperor
is still playing the fool

00:14:59.320 --> 00:15:00.800 line:80%
under Wei Yan's thumb.

00:15:00.880 --> 00:15:02.280 line:80%
Does he dare pick a fight with me?

00:15:05.760 --> 00:15:07.760 line:80%
His Majesty sits at the throne
since he was a child.

00:15:07.840 --> 00:15:10.120 line:80%
He has his authority usurped
by Chancellor Wei all these years.

00:15:10.200 --> 00:15:13.000 line:80%
By now, he must be desperate for power.

00:15:13.080 --> 00:15:15.200 line:80%
I don't think he'll let this slide.

00:15:15.800 --> 00:15:17.840 line:80%
If he doesn't want to sit on that throne,

00:15:17.920 --> 00:15:19.360 line:80%
I can find someone else to take his place.

00:15:20.600 --> 00:15:21.760 line:80%
As it happens, I have been

00:15:22.880 --> 00:15:24.480 line:80%
considering deposing the emperor.

00:15:26.880 --> 00:15:27.960 line:80%
Depose the emperor?

00:15:29.000 --> 00:15:29.840 line:80%
Are you serious?

00:15:37.840 --> 00:15:42.160 line:80%
I know the Dayin court
is too muddy to look at.

00:15:42.840 --> 00:15:45.440 line:80%
I know you don't want to serve
such a worthless ruler.

00:15:46.200 --> 00:15:47.040 line:80%
But if

00:15:47.720 --> 00:15:50.200 line:80%
we support the imperial grandson now,
give it a decade or two,

00:15:50.280 --> 00:15:53.680 line:80%
who's to say Yu Bao'er
won't turn into another Qi Sheng?

00:15:58.120 --> 00:16:00.160 line:80%
What Yu Bao'er becomes in the future,

00:16:00.240 --> 00:16:01.240 line:80%
I don't know.

00:16:02.160 --> 00:16:04.520 line:80%
But I will never become another Wei Yan.

00:16:08.080 --> 00:16:10.080 line:80%
Alright. By the way,

00:16:10.880 --> 00:16:12.080 line:80%
aren't you heading back to Jizhou Yamen?

00:16:12.840 --> 00:16:13.680 line:80%
What for?

00:16:15.680 --> 00:16:18.880 line:80%
That Li Huai'an
keeps visiting Mrs. Fan every other day.

00:16:18.960 --> 00:16:20.400 line:80%
You're really not worried?

00:16:25.000 --> 00:16:26.560 line:80%
Don't look at me like that.

00:16:27.080 --> 00:16:29.720 line:80%
They've already started calling each other
brother and sister, building rapport.

00:16:29.800 --> 00:16:32.240 line:80%
And when she's vulnerable,
he'll seize the opportunity.

00:16:32.320 --> 00:16:34.160 line:80%
-The most basic courtship tactic--
-Enough.

00:16:34.680 --> 00:16:36.520 line:80%
-You're the advanced one. Happy?
-I…

00:16:36.600 --> 00:16:37.440 line:80%
Mind your own business.

00:16:38.040 --> 00:16:38.960 line:80%
Report!

00:16:40.400 --> 00:16:41.560 line:80%
Marquis,

00:16:41.640 --> 00:16:44.040 line:80%
Sui Yuanqing, with the remaining enemy
from Chongzhou, is attacking us.

00:16:52.000 --> 00:16:53.120 line:80%
How many troops?

00:16:53.200 --> 00:16:54.760 line:80%
Just a few dozen soldiers,

00:16:54.840 --> 00:16:57.400 line:80%
charging the gate like madmen,
with no reinforcements behind them.

00:16:57.480 --> 00:16:59.440 line:80%
<i>Looks like they're here to die.</i>

00:17:06.480 --> 00:17:08.080 line:80%
Xie Zheng!

00:17:09.000 --> 00:17:11.399 line:80%
Come out, you coward!

00:17:12.520 --> 00:17:15.600 line:80%
Let's settle this today.

00:17:33.600 --> 00:17:35.440 line:80%
Why put yourself through this, Young Heir?

00:17:36.000 --> 00:17:37.440 line:80%
Why come all this way just to die?

00:17:40.720 --> 00:17:42.480 line:80%
Save your false pity.

00:17:43.080 --> 00:17:45.320 line:80%
You and Fan Changyu killed my father.

00:17:46.160 --> 00:17:47.520 line:80%
If I don't avenge him,

00:17:48.280 --> 00:17:49.520 line:80%
I'm not fit to live.

00:17:50.280 --> 00:17:51.680 line:80%
Prepare to die!

00:18:10.320 --> 00:18:13.840 line:20%
CHONGZHOU

00:18:14.440 --> 00:18:16.360 line:80%
If he believes it, fine.

00:18:16.440 --> 00:18:17.440 line:80%
If not,

00:18:18.480 --> 00:18:20.400 line:80%
destroy the Eastern Palace seal
on the spot.

00:18:20.480 --> 00:18:22.440 line:80%
It must never fall
into anyone else's hands.

00:18:22.960 --> 00:18:23.840 line:80%
Rest assured, Master.

00:18:30.080 --> 00:18:32.000 line:80%
LADY YIN, PRINCESS CHANGXIN

00:18:34.600 --> 00:18:35.440 line:80%
Mother?

00:18:41.880 --> 00:18:42.760 line:80%
What brings you here so suddenly?

00:18:44.160 --> 00:18:46.040 line:80%
Why do you treat your brother this way?

00:18:50.040 --> 00:18:53.320 line:80%
Yuanqing said he wanted to avenge Father.

00:18:54.120 --> 00:18:56.840 line:80%
That's filial piety. I couldn't stop him.

00:18:56.920 --> 00:18:58.000 line:80%
Filial piety?

00:18:58.080 --> 00:19:00.160 line:80%
Then why don't you go fulfill it yourself?

00:19:02.160 --> 00:19:04.520 line:80%
I have to stay
and take care of you, Mother.

00:19:05.400 --> 00:19:08.440 line:80%
You knew perfectly well the Marquis
of Wu'an is hunting you everywhere.

00:19:09.240 --> 00:19:11.320 line:80%
Yet you still stirred up Yuanqing
to avenge the prince.

00:19:11.400 --> 00:19:12.480 line:80%
How vicious.

00:19:20.000 --> 00:19:22.080 line:80%
Father never liked me.

00:19:23.680 --> 00:19:25.240 line:80%
And in your heart,

00:19:26.120 --> 00:19:27.600 line:80%
you always preferred
Yuanqing too, didn't you?

00:19:28.640 --> 00:19:29.600 line:80%
He's my son.

00:19:30.240 --> 00:19:31.360 line:80%
Of course I prefer him.

00:19:37.160 --> 00:19:38.080 line:80%
Mother,

00:19:39.640 --> 00:19:40.840 line:80%
what do you mean by that?

00:19:41.840 --> 00:19:43.000 line:80%
What mother

00:19:44.240 --> 00:19:47.040 line:80%
doesn't recognize her own child?

00:19:50.760 --> 00:19:53.240 line:80%
After that fire 17 years ago,

00:19:53.760 --> 00:19:55.320 line:80%
I brought you back.

00:19:57.600 --> 00:19:58.760 line:80%
At first,

00:19:59.800 --> 00:20:02.240 line:80%
seeing you so disfigured, my heart ached.

00:20:03.720 --> 00:20:07.320 line:80%
But when I learned you weren't Yuanhuai,
my heart ached even more.

00:20:12.400 --> 00:20:13.840 line:80%
So you knew all along.

00:20:18.160 --> 00:20:19.120 line:80%
Then,

00:20:19.760 --> 00:20:21.680 line:80%
why didn't you expose me
right then and there?

00:20:22.280 --> 00:20:23.320 line:80%
You were just

00:20:24.000 --> 00:20:25.600 line:80%
a small child then,

00:20:27.080 --> 00:20:29.960 line:80%
disfigured by the Crown Princess
just to stay alive.

00:20:30.920 --> 00:20:33.280 line:80%
While recovering in Changxin Manor,

00:20:33.360 --> 00:20:35.320 line:80%
you were so pitiful,

00:20:35.840 --> 00:20:38.240 line:80%
crying every day for your mother.

00:20:38.880 --> 00:20:41.160 line:80%
It softened my heart.

00:20:42.320 --> 00:20:43.240 line:80%
I thought,

00:20:44.360 --> 00:20:48.280 line:80%
since heaven let you live
in my son's place, then let you live well.

00:20:50.400 --> 00:20:53.800 line:80%
Consider it good karma for my Yuanhuai,
who died poorly and unjustly.

00:20:55.680 --> 00:20:57.400 line:80%
But I was wrong.

00:20:58.440 --> 00:21:00.320 line:80%
I thought you were just a lost dog.

00:21:00.400 --> 00:21:02.320 line:80%
Never imagined you were a starving wolf.

00:21:03.960 --> 00:21:05.680 line:80%
The greatest regret of my life

00:21:06.320 --> 00:21:07.920 line:80%
is taking a viper for a son,

00:21:08.720 --> 00:21:10.840 line:80%
becoming a mother to someone so venomous.

00:21:20.960 --> 00:21:26.680 line:80%
I am Qi Min, the Crown Prince's grandson
of the Eastern Palace.

00:21:33.800 --> 00:21:35.840 line:80%
Isn't being my mother

00:21:37.880 --> 00:21:38.760 line:80%
good enough for you?

00:21:44.160 --> 00:21:45.400 line:80%
I only have

00:21:46.120 --> 00:21:48.440 line:80%
Yuanqing and Yuanhuai as my sons.

00:21:49.960 --> 00:21:50.800 line:80%
You…

00:21:51.720 --> 00:21:52.840 line:80%
didn't deserve it!

00:22:32.920 --> 00:22:34.400 line:80%
Don't think that just because
you were kind to me,

00:22:35.640 --> 00:22:37.320 line:80%
I wouldn't dare kill you.

00:22:42.040 --> 00:22:44.240 line:80%
I… I gave you a chance.

00:22:47.640 --> 00:22:48.960 line:80%
But don't worry.

00:22:50.240 --> 00:22:54.000 line:80%
Xie Zheng will soon send Sui Yuanqing

00:22:54.080 --> 00:22:55.920 line:80%
to your side to fulfill his filial duty.

00:23:24.280 --> 00:23:27.760 line:80%
-Take her body. It might still be useful.
-Yes, sir.

00:23:36.600 --> 00:23:39.760 line:80%
HE

00:23:46.760 --> 00:23:48.000 line:80%
Come in.

00:23:52.800 --> 00:23:53.640 line:80%
Fan,

00:23:54.400 --> 00:23:56.640 line:80%
is it true your husband's going to be
the prince consort?

00:23:59.240 --> 00:24:00.880 line:80%
I thought Li Menkan
was marrying the princess.

00:24:00.960 --> 00:24:03.480 line:80%
Swapping grooms at the last minute
for something this big? Really?

00:24:04.560 --> 00:24:05.640 line:80%
I don't want to talk about this.

00:24:10.880 --> 00:24:11.720 line:80%
Alright.

00:24:17.720 --> 00:24:20.240 line:80%
You asked me to look into Sui Yuanhuai.
I found something.

00:24:22.200 --> 00:24:25.000 line:80%
Word is, tonight
they're sending out a large force.

00:24:25.080 --> 00:24:27.280 line:80%
Probably a massive manhunt
for that bastard.

00:24:28.560 --> 00:24:30.880 line:80%
That traitor's crafty,

00:24:31.400 --> 00:24:33.080 line:80%
slyer than a fox, sneakier than a weasel.

00:24:33.160 --> 00:24:34.520 line:80%
Even the troops your husband…

00:24:37.680 --> 00:24:39.600 line:80%
I mean Marquis of Wu'an

00:24:40.120 --> 00:24:42.000 line:80%
sent before, he's fooled them
multiple times.

00:24:44.520 --> 00:24:45.800 line:80%
He's muddying the waters.

00:24:47.160 --> 00:24:50.400 line:80%
When we're tired of searching,
he'll slip away.

00:24:53.880 --> 00:24:56.160 line:80%
So he's the son of some crown prince?

00:24:56.240 --> 00:24:57.320 line:80%
He could've…

00:24:58.760 --> 00:24:59.880 line:80%
could've been the emperor?

00:25:01.680 --> 00:25:03.080 line:80%
He could have been, once.

00:25:06.280 --> 00:25:08.520 line:80%
If he was so noble,

00:25:09.520 --> 00:25:11.960 line:80%
why would he pretend to be Sui Yuanhuai?

00:25:12.960 --> 00:25:15.240 line:80%
You've watched plenty of puppet plays.
You see it all the time, don't you?

00:25:15.840 --> 00:25:18.680 line:80%
Those nobles and lords,
scheming and fighting day in and day out.

00:25:19.200 --> 00:25:22.320 line:80%
It's all just greed for the throne
and the power, like flies after meat.

00:25:29.640 --> 00:25:30.800 line:80%
Fan, what are you looking at?

00:25:33.000 --> 00:25:34.400 line:80%
Qian once said

00:25:34.920 --> 00:25:36.720 line:80%
he's terrified of fire,

00:25:36.800 --> 00:25:38.560 line:80%
won't even light a lamp at night.

00:25:42.800 --> 00:25:44.720 line:80%
If that's the case,

00:25:45.960 --> 00:25:49.720 line:80%
we can look for houses
that should have lamps lit

00:25:50.480 --> 00:25:52.320 line:80%
but are pitch black.

00:25:52.400 --> 00:25:54.600 line:80%
That narrows down the search.

00:25:54.680 --> 00:25:56.760 line:80%
Why are you so set on finding him, though?

00:25:56.840 --> 00:25:58.840 line:80%
Just to get even for Ms. Yu?

00:26:00.960 --> 00:26:03.200 line:80%
You wouldn't understand. That man…

00:26:05.560 --> 00:26:07.320 line:80%
might be connected to something huge.

00:26:08.200 --> 00:26:10.680 line:80%
He once showed me a tiger tally.

00:26:10.760 --> 00:26:12.800 line:80%
Said it had something to do
with the Jinzhou tragedy.

00:26:12.880 --> 00:26:14.240 line:80%
It's connected to Jinzhou?

00:26:17.880 --> 00:26:19.880 line:80%
Then Yan Zheng must really
want to catch him

00:26:19.960 --> 00:26:21.200 line:80%
and get some answers.

00:26:22.400 --> 00:26:25.480 line:80%
Take my token. Tell them
there's an operation tonight.

00:26:25.560 --> 00:26:27.160 line:80%
Good training for our squad.

00:26:28.520 --> 00:26:29.400 line:80%
Got it.

00:27:01.520 --> 00:27:03.160 line:80%
-Someone's inside. Circle around.
-Okay.

00:27:10.240 --> 00:27:13.400 line:80%
GRACE IN HEART, PURITY IN FORM

00:27:30.040 --> 00:27:32.960 line:80%
Throat's been cut.
Looks like he's been dead a while.

00:27:34.160 --> 00:27:35.560 line:80%
How did he die?

00:27:37.960 --> 00:27:40.480 line:80%
Keep searching.
See if he has a tiger tally on him.

00:27:41.600 --> 00:27:42.640 line:80%
What tiger?

00:27:43.320 --> 00:27:45.640 line:80%
The tiger tally, like in the operas.
Just search him.

00:27:45.720 --> 00:27:46.640 line:80%
Okay.

00:28:16.720 --> 00:28:18.640 line:80%
Captain Fan Changyu
pays her respects to the Marquis.

00:28:21.160 --> 00:28:24.000 line:80%
Jin Changsheng pays his respects
to Prince Consort.

00:28:25.160 --> 00:28:27.480 line:80%
One more word and you're transferred
to the kitchen brigade.

00:28:28.640 --> 00:28:29.840 line:80%
Yes, Prince Consort.

00:28:30.560 --> 00:28:32.640 line:80%
I'm going, Prince Consort.

00:28:43.320 --> 00:28:44.480 line:80%
Sui Yuanhuai is dead.

00:28:45.600 --> 00:28:48.040 line:80%
That trail… is gone cold.

00:29:01.240 --> 00:29:03.200 line:80%
Sui Yuanhuai just died like that?

00:29:13.400 --> 00:29:14.920 line:80%
Looks a lot like Sui Yuanhuai.

00:29:17.280 --> 00:29:18.360 line:80%
All the evidence

00:29:19.120 --> 00:29:21.000 line:80%
points to him being dead.

00:29:22.160 --> 00:29:24.240 line:80%
But the more proof we have,
the more suspicious it gets.

00:29:24.960 --> 00:29:26.760 line:80%
Have Zhao Xun
come identify him personally.

00:29:27.280 --> 00:29:28.680 line:80%
Either way,

00:29:28.760 --> 00:29:31.160 line:80%
in this world,
Sui Yuanhuai no longer exists.

00:29:40.240 --> 00:29:42.320 line:80%
For years, there have been rumors

00:29:42.400 --> 00:29:44.960 line:80%
that Wei Yan held the tiger tally
by imperial order, seeking reinforcements

00:29:45.040 --> 00:29:46.440 line:80%
to break the siege at Jinzhou.

00:29:47.040 --> 00:29:49.680 line:80%
But on the way,
he suddenly turned back to the capital,

00:29:49.760 --> 00:29:50.960 line:80%
delaying the rescue.

00:29:53.520 --> 00:29:56.560 line:80%
Back then, Wei Qilin was transporting
grain but suddenly diverted to Chongzhou.

00:29:57.360 --> 00:29:59.000 line:80%
Wei Yan must have ordered him
to use the tiger tally

00:29:59.080 --> 00:30:00.280 line:80%
to mobilize troops there.

00:30:02.120 --> 00:30:03.360 line:80%
Yet in the end,

00:30:03.440 --> 00:30:05.200 line:80%
Prince Changxin never sent troops,

00:30:05.280 --> 00:30:06.640 line:80%
and the grain was delayed,

00:30:07.280 --> 00:30:08.560 line:80%
and no one knows why.

00:30:14.920 --> 00:30:17.440 line:80%
If Prince Changxin
saw the tiger tally back then

00:30:17.520 --> 00:30:19.600 line:80%
but claimed it was fake
and refused to send troops…

00:30:22.000 --> 00:30:25.440 line:80%
That would mean
Wei Qilin was truly wronged.

00:30:27.720 --> 00:30:28.720 line:80%
Seems like…

00:30:30.480 --> 00:30:32.840 line:80%
we're getting closer to the truth

00:30:33.880 --> 00:30:34.920 line:80%
about the Jinzhou tragedy.

00:30:35.520 --> 00:30:37.520 line:80%
If only we could find that tiger tally.

00:30:38.280 --> 00:30:40.280 line:80%
I searched Prince Changxin's belongings,

00:30:40.360 --> 00:30:42.640 line:80%
even Sui Yuanqing's personal belongings.

00:30:42.720 --> 00:30:43.720 line:80%
Nothing.

00:30:43.800 --> 00:30:45.000 line:80%
That Sui Yuanqing

00:30:45.080 --> 00:30:47.600 line:80%
would rather be tortured
than tell us where the tally is.

00:30:47.680 --> 00:30:49.280 line:80%
He even had the nerve to mock me.

00:30:49.880 --> 00:30:52.120 line:80%
I should've let Mrs. Fan
cut him down with one blow.

00:30:59.520 --> 00:31:00.360 line:80%
Marquis,

00:31:01.520 --> 00:31:03.360 line:80%
Zhao Xun has examined the body.

00:31:03.440 --> 00:31:04.280 line:80%
As you suspected,

00:31:04.360 --> 00:31:06.240 line:80%
the dead man isn't Sui Yuanhuai.

00:31:06.320 --> 00:31:07.960 line:80%
It's a double raised by Nanny Lan.

00:31:09.080 --> 00:31:10.480 line:80%
Not only does this double look like him,

00:31:11.080 --> 00:31:13.800 line:80%
every single burn scar on his body
was meticulously replicated.

00:31:14.480 --> 00:31:17.320 line:80%
And the woman who died in the manor,
has her identity been confirmed?

00:31:18.000 --> 00:31:19.160 line:80%
Zhao Xun identified her.

00:31:19.240 --> 00:31:20.440 line:80%
It's indeed Princess Changxin.

00:31:25.240 --> 00:31:28.240 line:80%
Killed his own foster mother
just to save himself.

00:31:29.400 --> 00:31:31.960 line:80%
To catch Sui Yuanhuai… No,

00:31:32.760 --> 00:31:34.400 line:80%
time to call him by his real name.

00:31:35.840 --> 00:31:37.200 line:80%
To catch Qi Min,

00:31:37.720 --> 00:31:39.440 line:80%
we'll need other leads.

00:31:40.200 --> 00:31:41.040 line:80%
Anything else?

00:31:43.160 --> 00:31:44.400 line:80%
All leads are dead ends.

00:31:45.320 --> 00:31:46.600 line:80%
Strange thing is,

00:31:46.680 --> 00:31:48.160 line:80%
every time we close in,

00:31:48.240 --> 00:31:49.800 line:80%
it's like they're ready for us.

00:31:50.520 --> 00:31:53.640 line:80%
I suspect
he's got eyes inside the command.

00:31:59.960 --> 00:32:02.800 line:80%
Looks like someone's being used as a pawn,

00:32:02.880 --> 00:32:04.920 line:80%
and they still think
they're fighting for justice.

00:32:06.600 --> 00:32:08.800 line:80%
Marquis, what's our next move?

00:32:10.960 --> 00:32:12.560 line:80%
Take Zhao Xun to see Sui Yuanqing.

00:32:13.080 --> 00:32:15.760 line:80%
Bring him the news of
Princess Changxin's death.

00:32:17.720 --> 00:32:19.680 line:80%
First squad, left. Second squad, right.

00:32:20.440 --> 00:32:21.880 line:80%
Spread out in a fan formation.

00:32:21.960 --> 00:32:22.800 line:80%
-Yes, sir.
-Yes, sir.

00:32:23.320 --> 00:32:24.440 line:80%
Check the bushes and rocks.

00:32:24.520 --> 00:32:27.120 line:80%
Copy that.Turn everything over.
Leave no spot untouched.

00:32:27.200 --> 00:32:28.360 line:80%
-Let's move.
-Check over there.

00:32:29.840 --> 00:32:31.320 line:80%
Nothing here.

00:32:31.400 --> 00:32:32.480 line:80%
Over there.

00:32:32.560 --> 00:32:33.400 line:80%
Follow me.

00:32:36.600 --> 00:32:38.560 line:80%
Master, it's the Xie army.

00:32:41.680 --> 00:32:43.440 line:80%
Sui Yuanqing wasn't enough.

00:32:44.560 --> 00:32:46.000 line:80%
Looks like the Marquis

00:32:46.520 --> 00:32:49.040 line:80%
won't stop until he has my head.

00:32:50.360 --> 00:32:51.680 line:80%
How's Madam's whereabouts?

00:32:52.520 --> 00:32:53.840 line:80%
No sign of her yet.

00:33:03.080 --> 00:33:05.960 line:80%
Master, the Li family took plenty from us,

00:33:06.040 --> 00:33:07.920 line:80%
and still no sign of their support.

00:33:08.000 --> 00:33:10.040 line:80%
They're letting the Marquis hunt us down.

00:33:10.120 --> 00:33:11.560 line:80%
You don't think they've turned on us?

00:33:13.640 --> 00:33:15.320 line:80%
If the Li family had turned,

00:33:15.400 --> 00:33:17.080 line:80%
we'd have been captured long ago.

00:33:18.560 --> 00:33:21.440 line:80%
But for being grandfather and grandson,

00:33:22.680 --> 00:33:26.840 line:80%
Grand Tutor Li and Li Huai'an
really aren't on the same page.

00:33:33.640 --> 00:33:34.960 line:80%
Almost time now.

00:33:35.040 --> 00:33:36.040 line:80%
He should be here soon,

00:33:36.880 --> 00:33:38.600 line:80%
if he believed me.

00:33:42.960 --> 00:33:43.840 line:80%
Master.

00:33:52.720 --> 00:33:54.360 line:80%
With Grand Tutor Li's help,

00:33:54.880 --> 00:33:56.880 line:80%
I'm most pleased.

00:34:34.320 --> 00:34:36.519 line:80%
-I need to tell you something.
-I don't want to hear it.

00:34:36.600 --> 00:34:37.920 line:80%
I just want you to know.

00:34:40.039 --> 00:34:42.039 line:80%
Anyone in this world
can be a prince consort.

00:34:42.880 --> 00:34:44.080 line:80%
But I, Xie Zheng, will not.

00:34:46.320 --> 00:34:48.039 line:80%
I already married into your family.

00:34:48.560 --> 00:34:50.439 line:80%
I belong only to Fan Changyu.

00:34:52.120 --> 00:34:53.320 line:80%
For this lifetime,

00:34:54.760 --> 00:34:55.999 line:80%
my heart is yours alone.

00:35:20.360 --> 00:35:21.240 line:80%
You…

00:35:25.080 --> 00:35:26.720 line:80%
Can you stop being so good to me?

00:35:27.760 --> 00:35:29.000 line:80%
The kinder you are,

00:35:30.680 --> 00:35:31.680 line:80%
the more uneasy I feel.

00:35:33.680 --> 00:35:35.320 line:80%
Is it because of who you are?

00:35:37.600 --> 00:35:38.720 line:80%
You know?

00:35:46.360 --> 00:35:47.640 line:80%
I saw that letter.

00:35:48.480 --> 00:35:49.840 line:80%
I know he was your father.

00:35:51.400 --> 00:35:52.920 line:80%
I also know what you're afraid of.

00:35:54.480 --> 00:35:56.080 line:80%
But I want you to know.

00:35:56.920 --> 00:35:58.600 line:80%
I'll keep investigating,

00:35:59.760 --> 00:36:01.040 line:80%
until I find the truth.

00:36:03.200 --> 00:36:04.520 line:80%
And on this path,

00:36:05.880 --> 00:36:06.960 line:80%
I want to be by your side.

00:36:21.080 --> 00:36:22.600 line:80%
But Sui Yuanhuai is dead.

00:36:23.440 --> 00:36:27.000 line:80%
What if the truth isn't what we think?

00:36:35.440 --> 00:36:36.560 line:80%
That's the second thing

00:36:37.520 --> 00:36:38.760 line:80%
I wanted to tell you.

00:36:39.600 --> 00:36:40.760 line:80%
I'm planning

00:36:42.960 --> 00:36:44.000 line:80%
to release Sui Yuanqing.

00:36:44.800 --> 00:36:45.760 line:80%
What?

00:37:02.480 --> 00:37:04.320 line:80%
-You may go.
-Yes.

00:37:09.320 --> 00:37:10.160 line:80%
Young Heir.

00:37:11.200 --> 00:37:12.840 line:80%
Zhao Xun.

00:37:12.920 --> 00:37:14.560 line:80%
You traitor!

00:37:14.640 --> 00:37:16.200 line:80%
You betrayed my big brother!

00:37:18.040 --> 00:37:18.920 line:80%
Young Heir.

00:37:19.680 --> 00:37:21.760 line:80%
It was your brother who betrayed you.

00:37:25.440 --> 00:37:26.680 line:80%
A traitor.

00:37:27.960 --> 00:37:30.120 line:80%
Seeing that my big brother
has already escaped,

00:37:30.840 --> 00:37:32.520 line:80%
you want to coax
a confession for the Marquis

00:37:33.400 --> 00:37:35.520 line:80%
and drive a wedge between us brothers.

00:37:36.320 --> 00:37:38.280 line:80%
Save your breath.

00:37:39.200 --> 00:37:40.920 line:80%
Even if I can't kill you today,

00:37:42.880 --> 00:37:45.320 line:80%
my brother will avenge me soon enough.

00:37:47.360 --> 00:37:51.000 line:80%
And Princess Changxin's death,
who will avenge her?

00:37:55.840 --> 00:37:57.000 line:80%
Mother is dead?

00:38:01.840 --> 00:38:03.440 line:80%
Marquis of Wu'an!

00:38:03.960 --> 00:38:05.400 line:80%
Some hero you are,

00:38:05.480 --> 00:38:08.080 line:80%
laying hands on a woman!

00:38:08.680 --> 00:38:11.120 line:80%
The one who killed the princess
wasn't the Marquis of Wu'an.

00:38:11.200 --> 00:38:12.400 line:80%
It was Sui Yuanhuai.

00:38:13.000 --> 00:38:13.840 line:80%
No.

00:38:14.400 --> 00:38:16.320 line:80%
We should call him Qi Min.

00:38:19.760 --> 00:38:21.080 line:80%
Who?

00:38:21.160 --> 00:38:22.320 line:80%
All these years,

00:38:22.840 --> 00:38:24.600 line:80%
your dear elder brother,

00:38:24.680 --> 00:38:26.120 line:80%
he isn't Sui Yuanhuai.

00:38:26.640 --> 00:38:27.960 line:80%
He's Qi Min,

00:38:28.560 --> 00:38:32.360 line:80%
the former Eastern Palace grandson,
killed by Prince Changxin.

00:38:33.120 --> 00:38:34.600 line:80%
The real Sui Yuanhuai

00:38:34.680 --> 00:38:36.800 line:80%
died 17 years ago,

00:38:36.880 --> 00:38:38.920 line:80%
in that fire at the Eastern Palace.

00:38:47.640 --> 00:38:48.560 line:80%
No.

00:38:51.640 --> 00:38:52.560 line:80%
Impossible.

00:38:56.400 --> 00:38:59.800 line:80%
You're just using me
to go after my brother.

00:39:00.840 --> 00:39:02.000 line:80%
Young Heir,

00:39:02.720 --> 00:39:03.920 line:80%
wake up.

00:39:04.960 --> 00:39:08.680 line:80%
Qi Min killed the princess
to fake his own death and escape.

00:39:11.920 --> 00:39:14.760 line:80%
He's already reclaimed his identity
as the imperial grandson.

00:39:15.560 --> 00:39:19.240 line:80%
He's Qi Min, the one who destroyed your
family and left Changxin Manor in ruins.

00:39:23.720 --> 00:39:24.560 line:80%
No…

00:39:25.920 --> 00:39:27.000 line:80%
It's not like that.

00:39:28.120 --> 00:39:29.240 line:80%
It's not like that.

00:39:32.640 --> 00:39:34.720 line:80%
Aren't you my brother's lackey?

00:39:35.880 --> 00:39:37.280 line:80%
Why are you telling me this?

00:39:37.880 --> 00:39:38.880 line:80%
That's right.

00:39:39.720 --> 00:39:41.760 line:80%
I used to follow Qi Min,

00:39:42.760 --> 00:39:44.640 line:80%
but that was for the sake
of the true imperial line.

00:39:45.840 --> 00:39:47.760 line:80%
He is brutal in his nature.

00:39:47.840 --> 00:39:49.560 line:80%
He's unfit to inherit the throne.

00:39:50.640 --> 00:39:51.920 line:80%
I was forced

00:39:53.360 --> 00:39:54.600 line:80%
to turn to the Marquis of Wu'an.

00:40:06.000 --> 00:40:07.520 line:80%
Sui Yuanhuai…

00:40:08.440 --> 00:40:09.400 line:80%
No…

00:40:10.080 --> 00:40:11.600 line:80%
Qi Min.

00:40:12.200 --> 00:40:14.280 line:80%
I'll tear you limb from limb.

00:40:14.800 --> 00:40:17.120 line:80%
Avenge my father and mother!

00:40:20.560 --> 00:40:21.520 line:80%
Young Heir.

00:40:22.480 --> 00:40:23.600 line:80%
I can let you go.

00:40:25.040 --> 00:40:26.000 line:80%
Let me go?

00:40:27.040 --> 00:40:27.920 line:80%
Why?

00:40:28.000 --> 00:40:29.600 line:80%
My mother, Nanny Lan,

00:40:30.680 --> 00:40:32.240 line:80%
raised Qi Min for years

00:40:33.000 --> 00:40:34.440 line:80%
and died by his hand.

00:40:36.600 --> 00:40:38.800 line:80%
I only regret I'm not strong enough.

00:40:38.880 --> 00:40:40.760 line:80%
If you can eliminate Qi Min,

00:40:41.280 --> 00:40:43.600 line:80%
both our vendettas will be settled.

00:40:51.560 --> 00:40:53.720 line:80%
You're nothing but a lackey.

00:40:57.960 --> 00:40:59.560 line:80%
But if you let me go,

00:41:01.200 --> 00:41:03.160 line:80%
I'll give you what you want.

00:41:12.560 --> 00:41:14.440 line:80%
Young Heir, this way.

00:41:24.040 --> 00:41:27.080 line:80%
You really think he can find Qi Min?

00:41:29.560 --> 00:41:31.520 line:80%
They've been brothers all these years.

00:41:32.040 --> 00:41:33.280 line:80%
He'll find a way.

00:41:34.640 --> 00:41:37.280 line:80%
19TH DAY, 7TH MONTH
17TH YEAR OF ZHENGPING

00:41:48.880 --> 00:41:50.800 line:80%
Sui Yuanqing escaped from prison.

00:41:51.840 --> 00:41:52.720 line:80%
What?

00:41:57.080 --> 00:41:59.840 line:80%
Get this to the post officer.
Send it to the capital now. No delays.

00:41:59.920 --> 00:42:00.760 line:80%
Yes, sir.

00:42:15.760 --> 00:42:18.120 line:80%
YAMEN

00:45:00.400 --> 00:45:03.480 line:80%
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
IN THE MAKING OF THIS EPISODE

00:45:03.560 --> 00:45:04.480 line:80%
Subtitle translation by: Wanjiao Song